    <title>Linux</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/07/24/Linux/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/07/24/Linux/</id>
    <published>2018-07-24T07:08:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-07-24T09:32:15.453Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><small><br>Linux 严格区分大小写<br>Linux 所有内容以文件形式保存 而且文件类型与文件后缀无关<br></small></p><p><strong>ls：</strong> 列出当前/相关目录下的所有文件和目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-a 显示所有文件  </span><br><span class="line">-l 详细信息显示  </span><br><span class="line">-d 查看目录属性</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>颜色类型<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">白色：普通文件</span><br><span class="line">蓝色：目录</span><br><span class="line">绿色：可执行文件</span><br><span class="line">红色：压缩文件</span><br><span class="line">浅蓝色：链接文件</span><br><span class="line">红色闪烁：链接的文件有问题</span><br><span class="line">黄色：设备文件</span><br><span class="line">灰色：其他文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>mkdir:</strong> 创建目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-p 递归创建  </span><br><span class="line">-m  自定义创建目录的权限 eg：mkdir -m 775 xxx  </span><br><span class="line">-v  显示创建目录的详细信息</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>pwd:</strong> 显示当前目录  </p><p><strong>rmdir:</strong> 删除空目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-v  显示执行过程  </span><br><span class="line">-p  若自父母删除后父目录为空则一并删除</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>rm:</strong> 删除文件<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-r 删除目录  </span><br><span class="line">-f 强行执行删除 不询问  </span><br><span class="line">-i  删除提示  </span><br><span class="line">-v  详细显示进行步骤</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>cp:</strong> 将源文件复制到目标文件，或将多个源文件复制到目标目录中<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-r -R  递归复制该目录及其子目录内容  </span><br><span class="line">-p     连同档案属性一起复制过去  </span><br><span class="line">-f     不询问强行复制  </span><br><span class="line">-s     生成快捷方式  </span><br><span class="line">-a     将档案所有特性一起复制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>mv:</strong> 剪切文件，改名<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-b  覆盖之前的备份  </span><br><span class="line">-f  如存在不询问而强制覆盖  </span><br><span class="line">-i  存在则询问是否覆盖  </span><br><span class="line">-u  较新才覆盖  </span><br><span class="line">-t  将多个源文件移动到统一目录下，目录参数在前，文件参数在后</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>scp:</strong> 在linux服务器之间复制文件和目录<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-v  详细显示输出具体情况   </span><br><span class="line">-r  递归复制整个目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>cd:</strong> 改变当前目（cd后面有空格）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-    返回上层目录   </span><br><span class="line">..   返回上层目录   </span><br><span class="line">回车  返回主目录   </span><br><span class="line">/    根目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>echo:</strong>  显示内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-n  输出后不换行   </span><br><span class="line">-e  遇到转义字符特殊处理</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>touch:</strong> 创建空文件（可同时创建多个文件）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg touch &quot;ic ab&quot; 一个文件   </span><br><span class="line">touch ic ab 两个文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>cat：</strong> 显示文件内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-n  显示行号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>tac:</strong> 反向显示内容   </p><p><strong>more:</strong>  分页显示内容<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">空格或f  翻页   </span><br><span class="line">enter 换行   </span><br><span class="line">q或Q 退出   </span><br><span class="line">+n        从第n行开始显示   </span><br><span class="line">-n        每次查看n行数据   </span><br><span class="line">+/String  搜索String字符串位置，从其前两行开始查看   </span><br><span class="line">-c        清屏再显示   </span><br><span class="line">-p        换页时清屏</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>less:</strong> 分页显示内容（可以往上翻  其他与more相同）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/加关键词  搜索  按n至下一个</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>head:</strong> 显示文件前几行<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-n 指定行数（不加默认10行）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>tail:</strong> 显示文件末尾几行<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-n 指定函数 （ 不加默认10行 ）</span><br><span class="line">-f 动态显示文件末尾内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>ln:</strong> 生成链接文件<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-s 创建软链接（ 软链接类似于windows中的快捷方式）</span><br><span class="line">不加s 创建硬链接</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>硬链接特征  </p><ul><li>拷贝cp-p加同步更新  </li><li>i节点与源文件相同  </li><li>不能跨分区  </li></ul><p><strong>chomd:</strong> 更改权限<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chomd &#123;ugoa&#125;&#123;+-=&#125;&#123;rwx&#125; 文件或目录    </span><br><span class="line">eg chomd u+x 文件名 &lt;!-- 对多个操作 用，分隔开--&gt;   </span><br><span class="line">用数字表示 r=4 w=2 x=1   </span><br><span class="line">eg chomd 640 文件名   </span><br><span class="line">-R 递归修改 &lt;!-- 对于子目录或文件 也是这个权限--&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-rw-r--r--   r读 w写 x执行</span><br><span class="line">第一个-是表示文件类型 -二进制文件 d目录 l软链接文件</span><br><span class="line">第2-4 u：所有者</span><br><span class="line">第5-7 g：所属组</span><br><span class="line">第8-10 o：其他人</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th></th><th>文件</th><th>目录</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>r</td><td>可以查看文件内容（cat,more,head,tail,less)</td><td>可以列出目录中的文件(ls)</td></tr><tr><td>w</td><td>可以修改文件内容（vim）</td><td>可以在目录中创建，删除文件（touch,mkdir,rmdir,rm)</td></tr><tr><td>x</td><td>可以这行文件（script command）</td><td>可以进入目录（cd）</td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>chown:</strong> 改变文件或目录的所有者（ 管理员才可以）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chowm [用户] [文件或目录]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>charp:</strong> 权限管理命令<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">改变文件或目录的所属组</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>umask:</strong> 显示，设置文件的缺省权限<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-s 以rwx形式显示新建文件缺省权限   </span><br><span class="line">默认目录755 文件644</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>find:</strong>  文件搜索<br>find [搜索范围] [匹配条件]<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg find /etc -name init （ 在etc中搜索init文件）</span><br><span class="line">*init* 模糊搜索   </span><br><span class="line">init??? ？代表一个字符 </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">-iname 不区分大小写  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">find / -size +204800 （ 数据块 一个数据块=0.5k ）</span><br><span class="line">在根目录下查找大于100mb的文件 </span><br><span class="line">+n 大于 -n小于 n 等于   </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">find /home -user shenchao </span><br><span class="line">在根目录下查找所有者为shenchao的文件  </span><br><span class="line"> -gourp 所属组...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">find /etc -cmin -5   </span><br><span class="line">在etc 下寻找5分钟内被修改过属性的文件和目录   </span><br><span class="line">-amin 访问时间</span><br><span class="line">-cmin 文件属性  </span><br><span class="line">-mmin 文件内容  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">find /etc -size +163840 -a -size 204800  </span><br><span class="line">在etc 下寻找大于80mb小于100mb的文件  </span><br><span class="line">-a 两个条件同时满足  </span><br><span class="line">-o 两个条件满足一个就行了    </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">find /etc -name inittab -exec ls -l &#123; &#125; \;  </span><br><span class="line">在etc下寻找inittab文件显示其详细信息   </span><br><span class="line">-exec或-ok 命令 &#123; &#125; \; 对搜索结果执行操作  </span><br><span class="line">-ok会询问确认  </span><br><span class="line">find -inum 31531 -exec rm &#123; &#125; \;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>locate:</strong> 在文件资料库中查找文件（快速查找）<br>locate 文件名<br>没有在文件资料库中的文件是找不到的<br>updatedb 更新资料库（不更新tmp中的文件）<br>locate -i 文件名 不区分大小写    </p><p><strong>which:</strong> 搜索命令所在目录以及别名信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eg which ls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>whereis:</strong> 搜索命令所在目录及帮助文件路径<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">whereis ls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>grep:</strong> 在文件中搜录字串匹配的行并且输出<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-i 不区分大小写  </span><br><span class="line">-v 排除指定字串   </span><br><span class="line">-c  只输出匹配行地计数</span><br><span class="line">-I  不区分大小写（只适用于单字符）</span><br><span class="line">-l  只显示文件名</span><br><span class="line">-v  显示不包含匹配文本的所有行</span><br><span class="line">grep -iv 关键字 文件地址  </span><br><span class="line">grep -iv ^#(#开头） /etc/inittab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>man:</strong> 获得帮助信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">man 命令或配置文件  </span><br><span class="line">man ls 查看ls命令的帮助信息   </span><br><span class="line">man services （不用加绝对路径 直接加名称）   </span><br><span class="line">查看配置文件services的帮助信息   </span><br><span class="line">如果命令与配置文件名字相同 优先查看命令的帮助信息  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">man 5 passwd 配置文件的帮助信息</span><br><span class="line">1 命令 5 配置文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>whatis:</strong> 命令简短信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">whatis 命令名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>apropos:</strong> 配置文件简短信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">apropos 配置文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>help:</strong> 获得shell内置命令的帮助信息（找不到路径的命令）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">help 命令</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>file:</strong> 判断文件类型</p><p><strong>zip:</strong>  压缩文件或目录 保留原文件<br>zip [-r] [压缩后文件名] [文件或目录]<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-r 压缩目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>unzip:</strong> 解压.zip的压缩文件<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">unzip 压缩文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>bzip2:</strong>  压缩文件 （压缩比大）<br>bzip2 [-k] [文件]<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-k 保留原文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>bunzip2:</strong>  解压<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-k 保留原压缩包    </span><br><span class="line">-#  压缩等级  </span><br><span class="line">-d  解压  </span><br><span class="line">-z  压缩  </span><br><span class="line">-c  将压缩过程产生的数据输出到屏幕上  </span><br><span class="line">-v  可以显示出原文件/压缩文件的压缩比等信息</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>gzip:</strong> 压缩文件，源文件都不再存在</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-d  进行解压缩</span><br><span class="line">-c  将压缩的数据输出到屏幕上</span><br><span class="line">-v  显示原文件/压缩文件的压缩比等信息</span><br><span class="line">-#  压缩等级，-1最快，但压缩比最差，-9最慢，压缩比最好</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>gunzip:</strong> 解压缩文件  </p><p><strong>tar:</strong> 打包目录压缩后文件格式为tar.gz 可以命名这个后缀便于区分<br>tar [-zcf] [压缩后文件名] [目录]<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-c 打包  </span><br><span class="line">-v 显示详细信息  </span><br><span class="line">-f 指定文件名  </span><br><span class="line">-z 打包同时压缩 -j 用bzip2压缩  </span><br><span class="line">-x 解包 </span><br><span class="line">-z 解压缩 -j 用bunzip2来解压</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>netstat:</strong> 显示网络相关信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-t tcp协议（3次握手）   </span><br><span class="line">-u udp协议 （快）  </span><br><span class="line">-l 监听  </span><br><span class="line">-r 路由  </span><br><span class="line">-n 显示ip地址和端口号  </span><br><span class="line">netstat -tlum 查看本机监听的端口  </span><br><span class="line">netstat -an 查看本机所有的网络连接  </span><br><span class="line">netstat -rn 查看本机的路由表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>setup:</strong> 配置网络<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">setup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>mount:</strong>  挂载设备<br>mount 设备文件名 挂载点</p><p><strong>umount:</strong> 卸载<br>umount 设备文件名<br><strong>write:</strong> 给用户发送信息 以ctrld结束<br>write 用户名（在线的）  </p><p><strong>wall:</strong> 发广播信息 给所有在线用户发信息<br>wall [message]</p><p><strong>ping:</strong>  测试网络连通性 （默认无限次 ctrilC终止）<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">-c 指定发送次数   </span><br><span class="line">ping -c 3 192.168.1.156</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>ifconfig:</strong>  查看和设置网卡信息<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ifconfig 查看 </span><br><span class="line">ifconfig 网卡名称 ip地址（临时改网络信息）</span><br><span class="line">eg ifconfig etho 192.168.256</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>last:</strong>  列出目前与过去登入系统的用户信息 </p>]]></content>
    
